runs.notes: Easy Run 8km at 6:30-7:00/km pace. Start very easy and progress to pace after 1-2km.
Long Run 16km at 6:15-6:45/km pace. Take water if temperature above 15C. Start easy and settle into pace after 2-3km.
Medium Long Run 10km at 6:30-6:45/km pace. Keep effort controlled throughout.
Quality Session: Total 9km as follows: 2km warmup (7:00/km pace), 4km continuous tempo (5:45-6:00/km pace), 3km cooldown (7:00+/km pace). Dynamic stretches before start.
Easy Run 7km at 6:30-7:00/km pace. Recovery effort - keep it relaxed.
